description: Seeks to track the performance of the FTSE Developed All Cap ex US Hedged to CAD Index to the extent possible and before fees and expenses. Invests primarily in the U.S.-domiciled Vanguard FTSE Developed Markets ETF. Foreign currency exposure hedged back to the Canadian dollar. Uses efficient, cost-effective index management techniques.
name: Vanguard FTSE Developed All Cap ex U.S. Index ETF (CAD-hedged)
